<h2 id="autonomous-vs-prompted-crons--new">Autonomous vs Prompted Crons ‚≠ź NEW</h2>

<p><strong>Key insight:</strong> There‚Äôs a critical difference between cron jobs that <em>prompt</em> you vs ones that <em>do the work</em>.</p>

<h3 id="two-architectures">Two Architectures</h3>

