<h3 id="4-verify-before-reporting-vbr">4. Verify Before Reporting (VBR)</h3>

<p><strong>The Law:</strong> ‚ÄúCode exists‚ÄĚ ‚Č† ‚Äúfeature works.‚ÄĚ Never report completion without end-to-end verification.</p>

<p><strong>Trigger:</strong> About to say ‚Äúdone‚ÄĚ, ‚Äúcomplete‚ÄĚ, ‚Äúfinished‚ÄĚ:</p>
